y \par \par \uc2  3. Loss of job \par \par \uc2  4. Death \par \par \uc2  The scheme will enhance savings, help in reducing inflation and provide a security net for individuals. \par \par \uc2  R.K. CHOPRA \par \par \uc2  Jakarta \par \par \uc2  Copyright 1998 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010924du3n008zc\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
